@NODE Search "Tech Guide/Commands"

     Search  [name]  [pattern]  [ucnlc]  [wild]  [byword]

              name  optional; name of file

           pattern  optional; text pattern to search for

             ucnlc  optional; uppercase characters does not equal lower
